oai_dc:dc.dc:title: "Indian Rock Cottage," Miss Mary Means, Beersheba Springs, Tennessee
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of the exterior of Indian Rock Cottage, a shop and eatery operated by Mary Means. Features a divided back and handwritten correspondence on reverse. A piece of tape covers the top portion of this postcard.
